{"id":310367,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-湖南电站开闸泄洪，一老兵被淹死家中/","date":"2013-08-24T17:02:57Z","modified":"2013-08-24T17:02:57Z","title":"维权网 | 湖南电站开闸泄洪，一老兵被淹死家中","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span> </span></p>\n<div><span> </span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员召平报道）今天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>24</span></span><span>日）本网信息员听到湖南永州市蓝山县的肖辉先生（电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>15167383886</span></span><span>）反映，因永州地方政府工作人员失职，水库管理部门泄洪没有及时保证沿途居民撤离，导致一老兵在家中活活被淹死的惨剧。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>肖先生说，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013</span></span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>14</span></span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>16</span></span><span>日，在湘南区域永州市蓝山县县城，连续两三天大雨，导致蓝山县城舜水河水位上涨，造成居住在舜水河河畔一带供销联社的居民受灾。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>16</span></span><span>日，舜水河上游万年桥水电站开闸泄洪，使得这场洪灾雪上加霜，致使住在供销联社居民区一楼</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>86</span></span><span>岁高龄老兵梁光生老先生来不及撤走，活生生淹殁在自己家中。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}